other_tests.findings: The uterus measures 6.0 x 2.0 x 4.1 cm. The endometrium is homogeneous and measures 3 mm. The ovaries are normal. The right ovary measures 3.1 x 2.9 cm and contains multiple follicles, the largest measuring 1.4 cm in longest dimension. Normal arterial and venous waveforms are seen. The left ovary measures 3.3 x 2.5 x 2.1 cm and contains multiple follicles. Appropriate arterial and venous waveforms are detected. The right lower quadrant was scanned and the appendix was not clearly seen. No free fluid is seen.
